high_descs: Turn around and head towards the stove.
Pick up the pan behind the kettle on the stove.
Turn left, head towards the black table, and face the black table as you stand next to the wall.
Place the plate behind the lettuce on the table.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Place the spoon on the pan.
anns.task_desc: Place a spoon on a plan to place it on the black table.

high_descs: Turn and take a few steps to the right and then face the stove.
Pick up the pan from the back burner.
Turn left and walk straight ahead to the chair and turn right to stand in front of the fridge. Turn left and take a couple steps towards the wall and turn left to face the table.
Place the pan on the left side in front of the fork and knife.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Stand the spoon up in the pan that is on the table.
anns.task_desc: To move the pan to the table while placing a spoon standing up on it.

high_descs: Turn around, go to the stove
Take the pan from the stove
Head to the left to the kitchen table
Put the pan on the table
Take the spoon from the table
Put the spoon in the pan
anns.task_desc: Put the pan on the table, put the spoon in the pan
